{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/marked/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Setting up marked.js","date":"May 14, 2024"},"html":"<h2>Introduction</h2>\n<p>The first issue I came accross upon after trying to set up my blog was that the markdown files were not being rendered properly. The images were not being displayed and the markdown was not being rendered. I had to find a way to render the markdown files properly.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 30.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"error-rendering\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/5a190/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/772e8/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 200w,\n/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/e17e5/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 400w,\n/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/5a190/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 800w,\n/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/c1b63/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 1200w,\n/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/29007/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 1600w,\n/static/0d285d065711aacf5e305dc3a4864ed0/1105b/2024-05-14-12.31.08PM.png 2940w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Solution</h2>\n<p>Eventually I was able to find a solution for the 'marked.js' library. I used the following code to render the markdown files properly.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x3C;script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js\">&#x3C;/script>\n</code></pre>\n<h2>Discussion</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>❓ Why did I choose marked.js?</p>\n<p>I chose marked.js because it is a fast markdown parser and compiler. I also found a lot of resources online that helped me set it up.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>❓ Why were the full image paths not working?</p>\n<p>The full image paths were not working because I was serving locally from a lower directory. The image paths weren't being recognized due to this.<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"docs\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/5a190/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/772e8/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 200w,\n/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/e17e5/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 400w,\n/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/5a190/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 800w,\n/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/c1b63/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 1200w,\n/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/29007/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 1600w,\n/static/dbe2ba8cfd47e74cacfd0fbf84ec64e6/820f7/2024-05-14-12.41.30PM.png 2126w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\nIn the image above, the image path is being recognized.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"docs\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/5a190/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/772e8/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 200w,\n/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/e17e5/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 400w,\n/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/5a190/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 800w,\n/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/c1b63/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 1200w,\n/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/29007/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 1600w,\n/static/8a08f642dedfdd3e3632c6942af71733/d5ef8/2024-05-14-12.44.02PM.png 2462w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span>\nHowever, in the image above, the image path is not being recognized despite having the same path in the link. This is due to the server being open in a higher directory.</p>\n</blockquote>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/marked/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}